<p>At HoloVault, we are a small collector-focused Pokémon TCG singles store. Please choose carefully before purchasing, as we generally do not accept returns or change-of-mind purchases.</p>
<p>Due to the nature of trading cards, collectables, sealed products, and condition-sensitive items, all sales are considered final unless an item arrives significantly different from its listing description.</p>

<h2>Condition &amp; listings</h2>
<p>We do our best to provide:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Accurate card photos</li>
  <li>Honest condition notes</li>
  <li>Clear descriptions</li>
  <li>Careful packaging</li>
</ul>
<p>Please review all photos and descriptions carefully before placing an order.</p>

<h2>Returns we may accept</h2>
<p>We may review return requests if:</p>
<ul>
  <li>The wrong item was sent</li>
  <li>The item arrives damaged in transit</li>
  <li>The item received is significantly different from the listing</li>
</ul>
<p>If there is an issue with your order, please contact us within <strong>48 hours of delivery</strong> with:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Your order number</li>
  <li>Photos of the item</li>
  <li>Photos of packaging if damaged during shipping</li>
</ul>

<h2>Non-returnable items</h2>
<p>We do not accept returns for:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Change of mind</li>
  <li>Incorrect purchases</li>
  <li>Minor condition differences</li>
  <li>Grading expectations</li>
  <li>Sealed product openings</li>
  <li>Buyer remorse</li>
</ul>

<h2>Shipping issues</h2>
<p>Once orders are handed to the shipping provider, delivery times are outside of our control. However, we will always do our best to assist if an issue arises.</p>

<p>For any order concerns, please <a href="/pages/contact">contact HoloVault</a> through the store contact page or email provided on the website.</p>
